        "rating": 5,
        "text": "American Gold Refinery in NYC is AWESOME!  Located in the Diamond District, AGR is professional, honest, and transparent in their business practice.  I watched as each piece was tested, and weighed and left with a sheet detailing exactly the amount  I was paid for the gold items I brought in by K type(10k, 14k, 18k), the weight I had of each type, the current price by penny weight, and the amount being paid for each accordingly.  Clear and easy to understand, I had no doubt surrounding the fairness of this transaction.  I highly recommend AGR to anyone looking to scrap their gold.  I would not hesitate to do business with them again.",
